reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater soft, comfortable, and lightweight, with one noting it's not scratchy.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute for fall family photos!
items.body: Obsessed with this EVALESS maroon cable-knit sweater! The texture and color are absolutely gorgeous — rich, warm, and perfect for fall family photos. It has that relaxed, slightly oversized fit that looks amazing with a variety of bottoms. The material feels luxe and soft against the skin, making it both stylish and comfy. Totally a must-have staple for the season! Read more
items.author: Simply Reviewed by K

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars A VERY PRETTY SWEATER, GREAT CHOICE AND A GREAT PRICE
items.body: THIS IS A VERY LIGHT GREY. FABRIC IS SOFT AND COZY. ANOTHER GREAT CHOICE FROM AMAZON Read more
items.author: Caroline A.

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice but runs large, may want to size down
items.body: Beautiful sweater, soft and stylish. Described as oversized but I just found it sloppy looking in my normal medium size, so I exchanged it for a small and it's perfect. Read more
items.author: kk

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful!
items.body: Cute and soft sweater. Haven’t worn it yet, but I’m looking forward to. The fit is nice. The price was right. Reminds me of a sweater a friend had many years ago that I always loved! I had to have it! Read more
items.author: PoodleMom

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Runs big, snag issues, very delicate
items.body: The media could not be loaded. I was needing something for family pictures and this was a nice looking sweater. It is lightweight and soft, but I think it runs big in size. I’m usually between a medium and a large so I went with a large and it seemed oversized for me. I’m 5 foot 6 inches and weigh 170 pounds. It also snags easily, so beware of that. I feel it will possibly pill in just a few wearing/washings. It seems to be pretty delicate. I had three snags on the back right hand side and one towards the front bottom. I did pull the thread through to the inside, but you can still see the snag line. Since I have worn it, I don’t know if I am able to return it. Read more
items.author: Norma Fitzwater

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value, soft and comfortable layer.
items.body: Soft, comfortable and I love the color. Great value for the price. The fold marks when taken from the bag it was shipped in were intense and it had a really unpleasant odor. But a few minutes in the dryer fixed both issues. This is lightweight, perfect for layering. Read more
items.author: MelissaJoy

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Softest sweater I have this season
items.body: I love the overall fit and feel of this sweater. I got a size L because I wanted to be a little more flowy, and it is not tight fitting which I prefer. Some highlights that I really enjoy is that the sleeves are very breathable and that the white sweater is not see-through. It is stretchy and I have washed it twice and there was no shrinkage or seams fraying. It is a good quality soft sweater. Read more
items.author: Felicia Rolison

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful versatile sweater
items.body: I usually wear an XL in tops, but had to return for large. Oh my stars: it’s beautiful with jeans as well as the 3 skirts I tried on with it today! It’s more on the lightweight side which I love & it’s not scratchy. It looked amazing with jeans & booties & chunky silver jewelry. Winner! Read more
items.author: Peter

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Blackish Green, Blue, Burgundy, Black, Light French Beige, Navy Blue, Dark Brown, Smoke Green, Parchment, Pink, White, Pinkish Purple, Duffel Green, Chestnut. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
